{"tid":250691,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"想十月去四川","createTime":"2017-05-20T09:29:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-18T07:19:30.000Z","uid":54001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"49e11841b1a426833ffcdb1c575e6a23ebb044d8","tid":250691,"uid":54001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T09:29:25.000Z","msg":"plan去四川十四日<br />\n睇咗幾多唔同嘅遊記<br />\n就覺得川西綫 幾啱我去<br />\n<br />\n第一天：成都－海螺溝<br />\n第二天：海螺溝一日 <br />\n第三天：海螺溝-康定-新都橋<br />\n第四天：(新都橋)雅江－稻城 <br />\n第五天：稻城-日瓦鄉-亞丁 <br />\n第六天：亞丁村-冲古寺-洛绒牛場-亞丁村-稻城 <br />\n第七天：稻城-雅江（新都橋） <br />\n第八天：雅江（新都橋）-丹巴 <br />\n第九天：丹巴-四姑娘山 <br />\n第十天：四姑娘山（长平溝一日） <br />\n第十一天：四姑娘山-汶川-茂县 <br />\n第十二天：茂縣-松潘-九寨溝<br />\n第十三天：搭九寨溝觀光車全天遊覽九寨溝，<br />\n宿九寨溝<br />\n第十四天：九寨溝&mdash;黄龍&mdash;茂縣<br />\n第十五天：茂縣&mdash;成都<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n求巴絲指教，狠批<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2df30cad49ef2c9f26cadab378a6ec7ec1adb5b","tid":250691,"uid":11283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T09:35:21.000Z","msg":"小心折多山個度高反<br />\n其他都無問題<br />\n環線大家都係咁行"},{"pid":"97c44ab839280d0021980153a5f3c6d65d3df1db","tid":250691,"uid":54001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T10:29:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>小心折多山個度高反<br />\n其他都無問題<br />\n環線大家都係咁行</blockquote><br />\n好的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n多謝巴打"},{"pid":"adeb0ee88b0dad2fef989784e55375da7ad6e95c","tid":250691,"uid":54001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T11:11:23.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"48a9d0873a34c942ecc2cb84ca217f34fb01a1c0","tid":250691,"uid":212473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T04:22:48.000Z","msg":"可唔可以留個tg問下你旅行嘅嘢<br />\n有意去四川"},{"pid":"ead2bd35eb6b9d05f7c7417a80f7feb5005f858b","tid":250691,"uid":54001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score"